### USER STORY 5: Payload Delivery and PDT Generation
### ========================================

### Step 1: Deliver Payload (Simulates pressure sensor activation)
POST http://localhost:8190/api/warehousing/payload-delivery/deliver
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licensePlate": "ABC-123",
  "rawMaterialName": "Gypsum",
  "warehouseNumber": "Warehouse-01",
  "payloadWeight": 18.5,
  "sellerId": "seller-001",
  "deliveryTime": "31/08/2025 20:30"
}

### Step 2: Retrieve PDT by License Plate
GET http://localhost:8190/api/warehousing/payload-delivery/pdt/ABC-123

### Step 3: Retrieve All PDTs
GET http://localhost:8190/api/warehousing/payload-delivery/pdt

